Solar Company Solyndra to File for Bankruptcy, Close Factories

-- B y   W i l l   W a d e
-- 
2011-08-31T16:08:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/solar-company-solyndra-to-file-for-bankruptcy-close-factories.html
Solyndra LLC, a U.S. maker of solar
modules, plans to file for bankruptcy.  The company will suspend manufacturing operations and
intends to file for Chapter 11 protection, Fremont, California-
based Solyndra said in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Wade at 
 wwade4@bloomberg.net  